This is a very small Script 

This script is for those programmers who work very hard . 
this script will remind Programmers in a certain time with their favourite song .
for example i want to drink water in every 3 hour so , this script will play a song in every 3 hour automatically and also show a popup in the computer screen so that we can change the sleep time or we can stop it .
we can simply shedule this script in shedule manager of our machine and it will run autometically at certain time (For Example At 9-5) .

the good thing is , it will also create logs for us as well so we can check it later .



In this Script am just using some random time but we can change it according to the need.
